Open up the Knockout documentation and click on that page right there.

20
00:01:03,370 --> 00:01:06,900
Read the page that talks about the foreach binding and have at it.

21
00:01:06,900 --> 00:01:08,210
Now, actually before you have at it,

22
00:01:08,210 --> 00:01:12,010
remember to commit your code in a repository at each step so

23
00:01:12,010 --> 00:01:14,740
you can always reset if you code yourself into a corner.

24
00:01:15,790 --> 00:01:19,570
And if you do get stuck or, for example, aren't sure how to get

25
00:01:19,570 --> 00:01:25,320
the actual array item into the bindings, read the documentation more thoroughly.

26
